# GitHub Copilot Repository Instructions

## Agentic behavior

When generating or editing code in this repository:

- Prefer small, reviewable changes.
- Follow existing project conventions.
- Do not invent commands, scripts, endpoints, or files.
- Avoid reading or suggesting changes to secrets, `.env`, private keys, credentials, dumps, or production logs.
- Add or update tests when behavior changes.
- Validate instructions against repository files.

